HEADWORD: anestrus
<hw>anestrus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A state or interval of sexual
inactivity between two periods of estrus; -- applies to nonhuman
mammals.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled <asp>anoestrus</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

